name: IBM i2 Analyze Developer Essentials
tagline: An open source repository for IBM i2 Analyze development
body:
Welcome to the GitHub home page for IBM i2 Analyze Developer Essentials. This repository contains example code, documentation, and discussion about customizing i2 Analyze.

Use the links above to access the repository, or to download its contents in TAR or ZIP format.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
